<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="disappear-vi">disappear <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌdɪsə'pɪə(r)/    美 /ˌdɪsə'pɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>消失；不见；失踪：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He walked away and disappeared into a crowd of people.
他走了，消失在人群中。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My pen was here a moment ago and now it has disappeared.
我的笔刚刚还在这儿，现在却不见了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>不复存在；灭绝：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That species disappeared in the Ice Age.
那个物种早在冰河时代就绝迹了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>disappearance /ˌdɪsə'pɪərəns/ n   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The symptoms of flu may be unpleasant, but they <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (消失) within a few days.  （2011 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. disappear  </p></div>